  <description type="morphology">Petioles densely long stipitate-glandular. Flowers: hypanthium free 1.1–2 mm,
        campanulate; petals greenish, white, or pink, narrower than sepals, margins nearly entire or
        finely dentate. 2n = 14.</description>
